=== 主要更新 ===

==== 9.0.1 ====
iOS 9.0.1於2015年9月23日發布。此更新修復了鬧鐘與計時器失效、暫停影片播放可能導致影格變形及設定輔助程式故障等問題<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://support.apple.com/kb/DL1842|title=Download iOS 9.0 - 9.3.5 Information|accessdate=2018-08-05|work=support.apple.com|language=en|archive-date=2019-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017121008/https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT208010|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macrumors.com/2015/09/23/apple-releases-ios-9-0-1/|title=Apple Releases iOS 9.0.1 With Multiple Bug Fixes|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2015-09-23|last=Clover|first=Juli|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027111806/http://www.macrumors.com/2015/09/23/apple-releases-ios-9-0-1/|archivedate=2016-10-27|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20150924002268-260412|title=蘋果推送iOS 9.0.1 修復少許Bug|last=中時電子報|newspaper=中時電子報|accessdate=2018-08-05|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180806145446/http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20150924002268-260412|archive-date=2018-08-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 9.0.2 ====
iOS 9.0.2於2015年9月30日發布。此更新修復了在接收通知時螢幕錯誤旋轉、部分使用者無法啟用[[iMessage|iMessage]]及[[iCloud|iCloud]]備份中斷等問題，並提升了[[Podcast|Podcast]]應用程式的穩定性<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT205284|title=關於 iOS 9.0.2 的安全性內容|newspaper=Apple Support|accessdate=2018-08-05|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180806145750/https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT205284|archive-date=2018-08-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macrumors.com/2015/09/30/apple-releases-ios-9-0-2/|title=Apple Releases iOS 9.0.2 With Bug Fixes, Performance Improvements|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2015-09-30|last=Clover|first=Juli|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027093655/http://www.macrumors.com/2015/09/30/apple-releases-ios-9-0-2/|archivedate=2016-10-27|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

==== 9.1 ====
