=== 安裝 ===
iOS 9安裝檔案大小較iOS 8減少了3倍以上<ref name=":4" />。另外若有需要，iOS 9還可以在安裝過程中移除部分應用程式以取得足夠的暫存空間，並在安裝完畢後自動回復<ref name="Installation">{{cite web|url=http://www.macrumors.com/2015/06/23/ios-9-app-delete-reinstall-os-update-feature/|title=iOS 9 Includes New Auto App Delete/Reinstall Feature for OS Updates on Devices With Insufficient Space|accessdate=2017-01-08|date=2015-06-23|last=Clover|first=Juli|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170103003255/http://www.macrumors.com/2015/06/23/ios-9-app-delete-reinstall-os-update-feature/|archivedate=2017-01-03|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2015/6/23/8834059/apple-ios-9-can-temporarily-delete-apps-before-updates|title=iOS 9 can temporarily delete apps to make room for software updates|accessdate=2017-01-08|date=2015-06-23|last=Welch|first=Chris|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170130003249/http://www.theverge.com/2015/6/23/8834059/apple-ios-9-can-temporarily-delete-apps-before-updates|archivedate=2017-01-30|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="Installation3">{{cite web|url=http://www.macrumors.com/2015/06/23/ios-9-app-delete-reinstall-os-update-feature/|title=iOS 9 Includes New Auto App Delete/Reinstall Feature for OS Updates on Devices With Insufficient Space|accessdate=2017-01-08|date=2015-06-23|last=Clover|first=Juli|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170103003255/http://www.macrumors.com/2015/06/23/ios-9-app-delete-reinstall-os-update-feature/|archivedate=2017-01-03|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.trustedreviews.com/news/apple-fixes-flaw-that-prevented-ios-9-app-thinning|title=Apple fixes flaw that prevented iOS 9 app-thinning|accessdate=2017-02-01|date=2015-10-06|last=Smith|first=Chris|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160125204526/http://www.trustedreviews.com/news/apple-fixes-flaw-that-prevented-ios-9-app-thinning|archivedate=2016-01-25|website=TrustedReviews|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

=== 效能 ===
iOS 9將原本只應用於遊戲中的[[Metal_(API)|Metal]]圖形技術擴展至系統中，更有效率地使用[[CPU|CPU]]和[[圖形處理器|GPU]]，提供更流暢的[[過場_(動畫)|動畫]]以及更出色的效能<ref name=":4" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/9-reasons-why-ios-9-will-make-your-old-iphone-feel-like-new-1519281|title=9 reasons why iOS 9 will make your old iPhone feel like new|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2015-09-10|last=McClelland|first=David|publisher=[[IBT_Media|IBT Media]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170420090946/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/9-reasons-why-ios-9-will-make-your-old-iphone-feel-like-new-1519281|archivedate=2017-04-20|website=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

=== 多工處理 ===
iOS 9為iPad新增了許多多工處理功能，包括Slide Over、Split View和子母畫面等<ref name=":4" />。[[Slide_Over|Slide Over]]功能使用戶不必離開正在使用的[[應用程式|應用程式]]，就能開啟第二個應用程式。第二個應用程式會出現於螢幕右側，約占螢幕大小的1/3；當開啟第二個應用程式時，原本的應用程式會暫停運作。用戶可快速搜尋網頁、回覆文字訊息，或在備忘錄中記下事項，然後滑動移開第二個應用程式，繼續原本的工作<ref name="MacRumors Multitasking">{{cite web|url=http://www.macrumors.com/2015/09/16/ios-9-split-screen-multitasking-ipad/|title=Inside iOS 9: Split-Screen Multitasking for the iPad|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2015-09-16|last=Clover|first=Juli|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229060035/http://www.macrumors.com/2015/09/16/ios-9-split-screen-multitasking-ipad/|archivedate=2016-12-29|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/how-to-use-the-ipads-new-slide-over-feature-in-ios-9/|title=How to use the iPad's new 'slide-over' feature in iOS 9|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2015-08-28|last=Cipriani|first=Jason|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160814023017/http://www.cnet.com/how-to/how-to-use-the-ipads-new-slide-over-feature-in-ios-9/|archivedate=2016-08-14|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

若將第二個應用程式繼續向右拉時，即會啟用Split View功能，進一步同時開啟和運作兩個應用程式。兩個應用程式將各佔螢幕大小的一半。用戶還可繼續調整應用程式所占面積，藉此重新進入Slide Over介面，甚至是關閉第一個應用程式、完全開啟第二個應用程式<ref name="MacRumors Multitasking" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/get-to-know-the-ipads-new-split-view-feature-in-ios-9/|title=Get to know the iPad's new 'split-view' feature in iOS 9|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2015-09-11|last=Cipriani|first=Jason|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222021122/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/get-to-know-the-ipads-new-split-view-feature-in-ios-9/|archivedate=2017-02-22|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

在使用FaceTime視訊或播放影片時，按下主畫面按鈕將啟用[[画中画|子母畫面]]功能，影像會縮小至螢幕右下角持續播放。用戶可以同時進行其它工作<ref name="MacRumors Multitasking" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/how-to-use-ios-9s-picture-in-picture-feature-with-youtube/|title=How to use iOS 9's picture-in-picture feature with YouTube|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2016-01-14|last=Cipriani|first=Jason|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170225035309/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/how-to-use-ios-9s-picture-in-picture-feature-with-youtube/|archivedate=2017-02-25|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

當用戶透過應用程式內連結前往另一個應用程式時，通知列左上角會出現返回上一應用程式的捷徑，點選即可回到原本的應用程式<ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/15/08/09/how-to-use-the-new-back-button-in-ios-9|title=How to use the new back button in iOS 9|accessdate=2017-04-06|date=2015-08-09|last=Oliver|first=Sam|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170406110541/http://appleinsider.com/articles/15/08/09/how-to-use-the-new-back-button-in-ios-9|archivedate=2017-04-06|website=AppleInsider|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

=== 電池 ===
iOS 9新增了[[低耗電模式|低耗電模式]]，當裝置電量低於20%時將自動啟用，藉由關閉背景應用程式及[[IBeacon|定位服務]]等耗電來源以增加續航力，至裝置電量超過80%時自動關閉。在iOS 9.3.2更新後，用戶也可以手動啟用模式<ref name=":4" /><ref name="Night Shift and Low Power Mode" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://bgr.com/2015/09/29/ios-9-batter-life-trick-low-power-mode/|title=This obvious iOS 9 trick helps your iPhone battery last much longer|accessdate=2017-10-12|date=2015-09-29|last=Smith|first=Chris|publisher=[[Penske_Media_Corporation|Penske Media Corporation]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171013013454/http://bgr.com/2015/09/29/ios-9-batter-life-trick-low-power-mode/|archivedate=2017-10-13|website=[[Boy_Genius_Report|BGR]]|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/how-to-use-low-power-mode-on-ios-9/|title=How to use low-power mode on iOS 9|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2015-07-16|last=Cipriani|first=Jason|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221090254/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/how-to-use-low-power-mode-on-ios-9/|archivedate=2016-12-21|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

另外，部分[[iPhone|iPhone]]現在可以透過感應環境光線和與桌面距離，決定收到通知時螢幕是否需要開啟<ref name=":4" />。

=== 3D Touch ===
iOS 9為[[iPhone_6s|iPhone 6s]]及[[iPhone_6s_Plus|iPhone 6s Plus]]引進了[[3D_Touch|3D Touch]]觸控技術，此技術與用於部分[[MacBook|Macbook]]之[[触摸板|觸控板]]上的[[Force_Touch|Force Touch]]技術相似。當用戶點選應用程式圖示、功能及內容時，裝置可根據用戶按壓螢幕的力道大小，決定應處理的動作<ref name=":5">{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160713010607/http://www.apple.com/tw/iphone-6s/3d-touch/|title=iPhone 6s - 3D Touch - Apple (台灣)|accessdate=2018-08-06|date=2016-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807081825/https://web.archive.org/web/20160713010607/http://www.apple.com/tw/iphone-6s/3d-touch/|archive-date=2018-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。輕壓應用程式圖示時，將顯示快捷選項<ref name=":5" />；透過Peek和Pop功能，部分應用程式還會提供細節預覽，若力道再加大，則會直接進入功能或開啟內容<ref name=":5" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macrumors.com/how-to/iphone-6s-3d-touch/|title=How to Use 3D Touch on iPhone 6s and 6s Plus|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2015-10-30|last=Gil|first=Lory|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161121223000/http://www.macrumors.com/how-to/iphone-6s-3d-touch/|archivedate=2016-11-21|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|deadurl=no}}</ref>。根據用戶按壓螢幕的力道大小，觸覺回饋也會有所變化<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/iphone-6s-iphone-6s-plus-first-look-hands-3d-touch-1519139|title=iPhone 6s and iPhone 6s Plus first look: Hands-on with 3D Touch|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2015-09-09|last=Arthur|first=Charles|publisher=[[IBT_Media|IBT Media]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161228061256/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/iphone-6s-iphone-6s-plus-first-look-hands-3d-touch-1519139|archivedate=2016-12-28|website=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

=== Night Shift ===
{{See also|Night Shift (應用程式)}}在iOS 9.3更新中，首次引進Night Shift顯示模式<ref name=":6" />。此模式與知名電腦軟體[[F.lux|F.lux]]功能相似，能偵測時間及[[地理位置|地理位置]]，自動調整[[色溫|色溫]]、減少藍光，維持用戶[[生理時鐘|生理時鐘]]正常<ref name=":6" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macrumors.com/2016/01/11/apple-ios-9-3-night-shift/|title=Apple Introduces New 'Night Shift' Feature in iOS 9.3|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2016-01-11|last=Clover|first=Juli|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161028063833/http://www.macrumors.com/2016/01/11/apple-ios-9-3-night-shift/|archivedate=2016-10-28|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/16/03/22/why-apples-night-shift-in-ios-93-will-help-you-get-a-better-nights-sleep|title=Why Apple's Night Shift in iOS 9.3 will help you get a better night's sleep|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2016-03-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161225221935/http://appleinsider.com/articles/16/03/22/why-apples-night-shift-in-ios-93-will-help-you-get-a-better-nights-sleep|archivedate=2016-12-25|website=AppleInsider|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name=":9">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/mar/21/ios-93-better-sleep-health-app-and-fingerprint-locking-for-notes|title=iOS 9.3 now available with Night Shift mode to help you sleep|accessdate=2017-02-18|date=2016-03-21|last=Gibbs|first=Samuel|publisher=[[Guardian_Media_Group|Guardian Media Group]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170218234639/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/mar/21/ios-93-better-sleep-health-app-and-fingerprint-locking-for-notes|archivedate=2017-02-18|website=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|deadurl=no}}</ref>；在iOS 9.3.2更新後，用戶也可以手動啟用模式，並在設定內調整細部色溫<ref name=":6" /><ref name="About Night Shift">{{cite web|url=http://www.macrumors.com/how-to/use-ios-9-3-night-shift-mode/|title=How to Use Night Shift Mode in iOS 9.3|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2016-01-14|last=Clover|first=Juli|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161120081201/http://www.macrumors.com/how-to/use-ios-9-3-night-shift-mode/|archivedate=2016-11-20|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|deadurl=no}}</ref>。由於硬體機能因素，Night Shift模式只支援搭載[[Apple_A7|蘋果A7]]以上[[CPU|CPU]]的裝置<ref name=":6" /><ref name="About Night Shift" />。

