=== 設定 ===
iOS 9為設定應用程式新增搜尋欄，簡化設定過程<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/2985017/ios/settings-in-ios-9-every-notable-change-you-need-to-know.html|title=Settings in iOS 9: Every notable change you need to know|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2015-09-21|last=Ochs|first=Susie|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161127171601/http://www.macworld.com/article/2985017/ios/settings-in-ios-9-every-notable-change-you-need-to-know.html|archivedate=2016-11-27|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.iphonehacks.com/2015/10/how-to-search-settings-on-iphone-ipad-in-ios-9.html|title=How to search Settings on iPhone or iPad in iOS 9|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2015-10-07|last=Obaizamomwan|first=Osas|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206201105/http://www.iphonehacks.com/2015/10/how-to-search-settings-on-iphone-ipad-in-ios-9.html|archivedate=2017-12-06|website=iPhoneHacks.com|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2015/9/18/9352327/new-ios-9-features-iphone-tips-tricks-guide|title=The best iOS 9 features you don't know about yet|accessdate=2017-03-26|date=2015-09-18|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109180831/http://www.theverge.com/2015/9/18/9352327/new-ios-9-features-iphone-tips-tricks-guide|archivedate=2017-01-09|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|deadurl=no}}</ref>；通知現在可以依照應用程式分類<ref name="Forbes 25">{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/gordonkelly/2015/09/19/apple-ios-9-secrets/|title=Apple iOS 9 Has 25 Great Secret Features|accessdate=2017-04-15|date=2015-09-19|last=Kelly|first=Gordon|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415105224/https://www.forbes.com/sites/gordonkelly/2015/09/19/apple-ios-9-secrets/|archivedate=2017-04-15|website=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/15/09/22/ios-9-tips-display-notification-center-alerts-individually-by-time|title=iOS 9 tips: Free Notification Center alerts from app groupings|accessdate=2017-04-15|date=2015-09-22|last=Edwards|first=Marty|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415200417/http://appleinsider.com/articles/15/09/22/ios-9-tips-display-notification-center-alerts-individually-by-time|archivedate=2017-04-15|website=AppleInsider|deadurl=no}}</ref>；用戶還可以搖晃裝置以還原操作<ref name="Redmond 45">{{cite web|url=http://www.redmondpie.com/the-hidden-ios-9-features-apple-didnt-tell-you-about/|title=The 45 Hidden iOS 9 Features Apple Didn’t Tell You About|accessdate=2017-04-15|date=2015-06-16|last=Ghani|first=Uzair|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415104427/http://www.redmondpie.com/the-hidden-ios-9-features-apple-didnt-tell-you-about/|archivedate=2017-04-15|website=Redmond Pie|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

