=== 訊息 ===
{{Main|iMessage}}
現在用戶可以搜尋並標記訊息內文<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/tech/2015/09/17/10-more-hidden-features-in-ios.html|title=10 more hidden features in iOS 9|accessdate=2017-03-26|date=2015-09-17|last=Epstein|first=Zach|publisher=[[Fox_Entertainment_Group|Fox Entertainment Group]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170327081731/http://www.foxnews.com/tech/2015/09/17/10-more-hidden-features-in-ios.html|archivedate=2017-03-27|website=[[Fox_News|Fox News]]|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

