== 問題 ==

=== 「錯誤53」裝置磚化問題 ===
2016年2月，大批經第三方維修商更換過零件（尤其是用於[[Touch_ID|Touch ID]]的指紋辨識器）的裝置，在升級至iOS 9後竟當機[[砖_(电子设备)|磚化]]。此問題被稱為「錯誤53」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/jaymcgregor/2016/02/05/iphone-6-killing-error-53-highlights-big-ios-9-problem|title=iPhone 6 Killing 'Error 53' Highlights Big iOS 9 Problem|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2016-02-05|last=McGregor|first=Jay|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222085520/http://www.forbes.com/sites/jaymcgregor/2016/02/05/iphone-6-killing-error-53-highlights-big-ios-9-problem/|archivedate=2016-12-22|website=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/money/2016/feb/05/error-53-apple-iphone-software-update-handset-worthless-third-party-repair|title='Error 53' fury mounts as Apple software update threatens to kill your iPhone 6|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2016-02-05|last=Brignall|first=Miles|publisher=[[Guardian_Media_Group|Guardian Media Group]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222040915/https://www.theguardian.com/money/2016/feb/05/error-53-apple-iphone-software-update-handset-worthless-third-party-repair|archivedate=2016-12-22|website=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.gq.com.tw/gadget/3c/content-26269.html|title=iPhone 6 感染error 53大瘟疫|last=Mo|first=Jimmy|newspaper=GQ瀟灑男人網|accessdate=2018-08-07|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2018-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807124856/https://www.gq.com.tw/gadget/3c/content-26269.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據第三方維修團隊[[iFixit|iFixit]]表示，「錯誤53」僅會出現於[[iPhone_6|iPhone 6]]及[[iPhone_6_Plus|iPhone 6 Plus]]上<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ifixit.org/blog/7889/whats-up-with-error-53/|title=What’s Up With Error 53?|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2016-02-05|last=Wiens|first=Kyle|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122143259/http://ifixit.org/blog/7889/whats-up-with-error-53/|archivedate=2016-11-22|website=[[iFixIt|iFixIt]]|deadurl=no}}</ref>。[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]隨後發布官方聲明表示：「當裝置未通過安全測試時，就會出現錯誤53。此測試的目的，是在裝置出廠前檢查Touch ID是否運作正常，其用意不是要影響客戶。」<ref name=":13">{{Cite news|url=https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT205628|title=如果在更新或回復 iPhone 或 iPad 時看到錯誤 53|newspaper=Apple Support|accessdate=2018-08-07|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2018-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807124831/https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT205628|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2016/02/05/apple-iphone-error-53/|title=Apple says the iPhone-breaking Error 53 is a security measure|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2016-02-05|last=Velazco|first=Chris|publisher=[[AOL|AOL]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022180457/https://www.engadget.com/2016/02/05/apple-iphone-error-53/|archivedate=2016-10-22|website=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ifanr.com/618011|title=iPhone 上出现了“五三”变砖危机，苹果却说这不是我该背的锅 {{!}} 爱范儿|accessdate=2018-08-07|work=www.ifanr.com|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2018-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807155347/http://www.ifanr.com/618011|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在iOS 9.2.1更新中修正了此問題<ref name=":13" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.techbang.com/posts/41497-push-the-apple-system-update-finally-resolved-error-53-brick-crisis|title=Apple 推送系統更新，終於解決「Error 53」變磚危機！ {{!}} T客邦|date=2016-02-19|newspaper=T客邦 - 我只推薦好東西|accessdate=2018-08-07|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2018-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807124945/https://www.techbang.com/posts/41497-push-the-apple-system-update-finally-resolved-error-53-brick-crisis|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="9.2.1 error 53 fixed" />，不過仍引發部分用戶不滿<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/123979|title=蘋果因Error 53遭澳洲法院判罰900萬澳幣|newspaper=iThome|accessdate=2018-08-07|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2018-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807125122/https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/123979|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 日期設定異常問題 ===
{{See also|UNIX时间#Unix負時間導致部分iPhone手機無法啟動}}2016年2月，一個重大漏洞被發現，由於裝置處理[[UNIX時間|UNIX時間]]不當，只要用戶手動將裝置日期設置為1970年5月前，即會導致崩潰<ref name=":14">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/feb/12/setting-the-date-to-1-january-1970-will-brick-your-iphone-ipad-or-ipod-touch|title=Setting the date to 1 January 1970 will brick your iPhone, iPad or iPod touch|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2016-02-12|last=Gibbs|first=Samuel|publisher=[[Guardian_Media_Group|Guardian Media Group]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221152315/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/feb/12/setting-the-date-to-1-january-1970-will-brick-your-iphone-ipad-or-ipod-touch|archivedate=2016-12-21|website=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.zhihu.com/question/40316064/answer/86223495|title=为什么把部分苹果设备的系统时间调整为1970.1.1，重启后就会变砖？ - 知乎|accessdate=2018-08-07|work=www.zhihu.com|language=zh|archive-date=2021-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211008145426/https://www.zhihu.com/question/40316064/answer/86223495}}</ref><ref name=":15">{{Cite news|url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/it/2016-02-16/doc-ifxpmpqt1264736.shtml|title=苹果确认iPhone/iPad时间设置不对会变砖问题|accessdate=2018-08-07|archive-date=2019-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502104822/http://tech.sina.com.cn/it/2016-02-16/doc-ifxpmpqt1264736.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://ck101.com/thread-3453951-1-1.html|title=蘋果承認iPhone調至1970年1月1日會死機！原因竟然是....|last=ck101.com|newspaper=卡提諾論壇|accessdate=2018-08-07|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807155421/https://ck101.com/thread-3453951-1-1.html|archive-date=2018-08-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此問題僅發生於搭載64位元[[中央处理器|處理器]]，即[[蘋果A7|蘋果A7]]以上處理器的裝置<ref name=":14" /><ref name=":15" />。蘋果在隨後的iOS 9.3更新中，將時間禁止調整到2000年以前，解決此問題<ref name="1970 Bug Fix and new Notes app" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://mrmad.com.tw/ios-1970-1-1-iphone-ipad-solution|title=注意！將iOS時間改為1970年1月1日就能讓iPhone與iPad死機 （含解決辦法） - 瘋先生|date=2016-02-12|newspaper=瘋先生|accessdate=2018-08-07|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2018-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807125153/https://mrmad.com.tw/ios-1970-1-1-iphone-ipad-solution|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== iPad Pro磚化問題 ===
